snippet.title: Rocket League Sideswipe Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the Rocket League Sideswipe Cinematic Trailer! Visit https://sideswipe.rocketleague.com for more details.

Get charged up for Rocket League Sideswipe, the new standalone mobile game from Psyonix! Download now on iOS and Android and get in the game from anywhere. 

Rocket League Sideswipe features fast-paced, arcade-style action with intuitive touch controls and controller support. Hit your boost to go faster, or use it to get off the ground and into the air to pull off some amazing aerial maneuvers. Enjoy Private Matches with friends, or play Competitive Matches online with players around the world. Climb your way up the Competitive Ranks, and even crack the worldwide leaderboard!

Download: https://rl.gg/PlayNow

Follow us at https://www.Twitter.com/RLSideswipe

We worked with Anamanaguchi, one of the main artists from Sideswipe's soundtrack, to bring Van Halen's 80s Classic 'Jump' into the Sideswipe universe. Listen to the song in the trailer! 
#RocketLeague #RocketLeagueSideswipe #RocketLeagueSideswipeTrailer
